---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="California Rideshare Accident Lawyers | Reardon Injury Law" description="Injured in an Uber or Lyft accident in California? Reardon Injury Law navigates complex rideshare insurance and fights for your compensation. Free consultation." bodyClass="body-2" currentPage="practice-areas">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div style="background: #141415; padding: 60px 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(238,186,107,0.2);">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container" style="max-width: 900px;">
        <h1 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">California Rideshare Accident Lawyers</h1>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;">Uber and Lyft accidents involve complex insurance disputes. We cut through the confusion and get you compensated.</p>
        <a href="tel:6575227122" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eeba6b 0%, #d4a84f 100%); color: #141415; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px;">Call (657) 522-7122 – Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
    <section class="sectionnn" style="padding: 80px 20px; background-color: #141415;">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container" style="max-width: 1100px;">
        <h2 class="text-headings" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">Why Choose Reardon Injury Law?</h2>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px;">
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/rideshare.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> Rideshare Insurance Expertise</h3>
            <p>Uber and Lyft accidents involve multiple insurance policies that change based on the driver's status. We know exactly which policy applies and how to maximize your claim.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/medical-expertise.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> Medical Expertise</h3>
            <p>John Reardon's 20+ years as a chiropractor means he understands soft tissue injuries, whiplash, and concussions at a clinical level — common injuries in rideshare collisions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/arrows-cycle.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> Handles Complex Claims</h3>
            <p>Rideshare accidents often involve multiple parties — the driver, the rideshare company, other motorists, and several insurance carriers. We untangle the complexity to protect your rights.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/aggressive-representation.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> Aggressive Negotiation</h3>
            <p>Rideshare companies and their insurers have teams of lawyers working to minimize payouts. We fight back aggressively and don't accept lowball settlement offers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/money.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> No Fees Unless We Win</h3>
            <p>You pay nothing upfront and nothing out of pocket. We work on contingency — our fee comes only from the compensation we recover for you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="practice-area-card">
            <h3><img src="/images/icons/scales.svg" alt="" style="width:40px;height:40px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"> Proven Results</h3>
            <p>We've recovered millions for accident victims across California. Our track record of success gives us leverage when negotiating with rideshare companies and their insurers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Common Injuries Section -->
    <section class="sectionnn" style="padding: 80px 20px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e1e1f 0%, #141415 100%);">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container" style="max-width: 900px;">
        <h2 class="text-headings sr-up" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">Rideshare Accident Injuries & Cases We Handle</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); text-align: center; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; margin-bottom: 40px;">Uber and Lyft accidents create unique legal challenges. We help victims in all rideshare scenarios:</p>

        <div class="sr-stagger" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;">
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/whiplash.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Whiplash & Soft Tissue</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Rear-end collisions are common in rideshare scenarios. Whiplash and soft tissue injuries can cause chronic pain that lasts months or years without proper treatment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/brain.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Head & Brain Injuries</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Rideshare passengers often aren't braced for impact. Concussions and traumatic brain injuries can affect memory, concentration, and quality of life — sometimes permanently.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/spine.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Back & Spinal Injuries</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Herniated discs, vertebral fractures, and spinal cord damage can result from the sudden impact forces in rideshare collisions, potentially causing permanent disability.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/bone.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Broken Bones</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Fractured wrists, ribs, legs, and collarbones are common when rideshare vehicles are struck. These injuries often require surgery and extensive rehabilitation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/shield.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Internal Injuries</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Seatbelt injuries, internal bleeding, and organ damage may not show symptoms immediately but can be life-threatening. Our medical background helps identify these hidden injuries.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sr-child" style="background: rgba(238,186,107,0.1); border-left: 4px solid #eeba6b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <img src="/images/icons/pain.svg" alt="" style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;">
            <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px;">Psychological Trauma & PTSD</h4>
            <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Rideshare accidents can cause lasting anxiety, PTSD, and fear of riding in vehicles. These psychological injuries are real and compensable under California law.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What to Do After an Accident -->
    <section class="sectionnn" style="padding: 80px 20px; background-color: #141415;">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container" style="max-width: 900px;">
        <h2 class="text-headings sr-up" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">What to Do After a Rideshare Accident</h2>

        <div class="sr-stagger" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 25px;">
          <div class="sr-child" style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="background: #eeba6b; color: #141415; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; min-width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">1</div>
            <div>
              <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 8px;">Screenshot the Trip in the App</h4>
              <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">Before closing anything, take screenshots of your active trip, the driver's information, and the route. This evidence is critical for proving rideshare involvement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="sr-child" style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="background: #eeba6b; color: #141415; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; min-width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">2</div>
            <div>
              <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 8px;">Seek Medical Care</h4>
              <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">Get medical attention immediately. Many injuries don't show symptoms right away. Medical records from the day of the accident are crucial evidence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="sr-child" style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="background: #eeba6b; color: #141415; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; min-width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">3</div>
            <div>
              <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 8px;">Report to Uber/Lyft AND Get a Lawyer</h4>
              <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">Report the accident through the app, but do NOT give detailed statements to their insurance without legal counsel. Their adjusters work to minimize payouts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="sr-child" style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="background: #eeba6b; color: #141415; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; min-width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">4</div>
            <div>
              <h4 style="color: #eeba6b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 8px;">Call Reardon Injury Law</h4>
              <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">Rideshare cases are time-sensitive. Insurance companies move fast to protect their interests. You need an attorney fighting for yours just as quickly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Form Section -->
    <section class="form" style="padding: 80px 20px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e1e1f 0%, #141415 100%);">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-22 w-container" style="max-width: 600px;">
        <div class="cta-header">
          <h2 class="cta-headerr sr-up" style="color: #eeba6b; text-align: center;">Get Your Free Case Review</h2>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
          <div class="textblockk" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Tell us about your rideshare accident. We'll review your case and call you back within 24 hours.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="w-form sr-up">
            <form id="rideshare-accident-form" name="Rideshare Accident Form" data-name="Rideshare Accident Form" method="get" class="form-2">
              <label for="name-rideshare" class="field-label-2">Name</label>
              <input class="text-field w-input" maxlength="256" name="name" data-name="Name" placeholder="Your full name" type="text" id="name-rideshare" required="">

              <label for="email-rideshare" class="field-label">Email Address</label>
              <input class="text-field-2 w-input" maxlength="256" name="email" data-name="Email" placeholder="your@email.com" type="email" id="email-rideshare" required="">

              <label for="phone-rideshare" class="field-label">Phone Number</label>
              <input class="text-field-2 w-input" maxlength="256" name="phone" data-name="Phone" placeholder="(555) 123-4567" type="tel" id="phone-rideshare" required="">

              <label for="message-rideshare" class="field-label">Tell Us About Your Accident</label>
              <textarea class="text-field-2 w-input" maxlength="2000" name="message" data-name="Message" placeholder="When did the accident happen? Were you a passenger, driver, or pedestrian?" id="message-rideshare" required="" style="min-height: 120px;"></textarea>

              <input type="submit" data-wait="Please wait..." class="submit-button w-button" value="Request Free Consultation">
            </form>
            <div class="w-form-done">
              <div>Thank you! We'll contact you within 24 hours.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-form-fail">
              <div>Oops! Something went wrong. Please call us directly at (657) 522-7122.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
